data.description: Discover the charm of 4137 Lynx Ln, Jonesboro, AR! This meticulously crafted all-brick home in the sought-after Bobcat Meadows subdivision spans 1846 sqft, showcasing tall ceilings and beautiful flooring that create an inviting atmosphere in the open floor plan. A rock gas fireplace adds warmth to the living area, while the kitchen delights with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and chic white cabinets. The master suite is a true retreat, featuring his and hers walk-in closets, a luxurious walk-in tile shower, and a double vanity in the master bath. Large windows flood the home with abundant natural light, and the screened-in back porch invites outdoor enjoyment year-round. With a 6-foot privacy-fenced backyard, this home seamlessly combines modern comfort and elegance in a fantastic location. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!  ***seller will install new gas log insert with acceptable offer***
